cat("Dear Aliens, \nGreetings from Earth! \nWe are from a planet that is 92.96 million miles away from the Sun. \nThere are many creatures living on Earth and we are one of them who call ourselves 'human-beings'. \nThere are 7.4 billion of us living on earth and we are quite different from one another. \nAlthough some of us are very aggressive, most of us are peace-loving. \nWe would love to be friends with you. \nWhat is live like on your planet? \nPlease tell us more about it! \nIt would be really great if you could reply to this message! \nBest, \nZeyan")